div.div: Feeding time (seconds of feeder use per 10 hours of recording time) spent by individual birds at each feeder (see characteristics in Table 1).

fn.p: Only 38 individual birds for which at least 10 visits to feeders were obtained are shown (i.e., those included in the statistical analyses). Individuals are numbered within specie. Cc: Cyanistes caeruleus, Lc: Lophophanes cristatus, Se: Sitta europaea, Pm: Parus major, Pa: Periparus ater.
